info.additionalInfo:
Include the javascript below in a bookmarklet or user script to toggle between mobile and full sites.

javascript:window.location.hostname.match(".wik")&&(window.location.hostname=window.location.hostname.match(".m.")?window.location.hostname.replace(".m.","."):window.location.hostname.replace(".wik",".m.wik"));

<a href="http://jamesmclendon.com">jamesmclendon.com</a>

style.css:
@-moz-document regexp('.*\.m\.wik.*\.org') {
/* Mobile Wikipedia

- serif
- increase font size
- increase line height
- reduce measure
- underline links
- works on most mobile Wikimedia sites (Wikipedia, Wiktionary, Wikiquote, etc.)

jamesmclendon.com */

body {
	font-family: Georgia, serif;
	line-height: 1.4;
	max-width: 45em;
	margin: auto;
}

.overlay {
	position: fixed;
	left: 0;
	width: 100%;
}

a { text-decoration: underline; }

}
